   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Adopt a Forest Guard &amp; Save Colombia&apos;s Wildlife</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Deforestation has skyrocketed in Colombia, destroying habitat and driving wildlife to the edge of extinction. To combat this threat, dozens of committed forest guards stand at the front lines of conservation, defending over 150,000 acres of rainforests and vulnerable habitat for endangered species at 27 nature reserves owned and managed by ProAves. Your donation will ensure vital support for our forest guards to secure the reserves, monitor threatened species, and educate local communities.</narrative>
  </description>
